net.sourceforge.waters.model.marshaller

Class ProductDESToModuleUnmarshaller

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.model.marshaller.ProductDESToModuleUnmarshaller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProxyUnmarshaller<ModuleProxy>

    public class ProductDESToModuleUnmarshaller
extends Object
implements ProxyUnmarshaller<ModuleProxy>
    A utility to load a product DES (.wdes) file as a module. This marshaller combines a JAXBProductDESMarshaller with a ProductDESImporter to load a product DES and directly as a module.
    Author:
    Robi Malik
